data.description: MOVE IN READY 4 BEDROOM 2 BATH FRESH home with MASSIVE fully engineered fenced area for RV PARKING, Casita or Cottage. NO HOA, all the freedoms of a .24 acre lot. Completely updated with excellent taste, from the accent Coronado exterior of this home, through security gate & beveled glass front door. Stepping down in to living area with traditional working granite fire place. Enter a freshly painted throughout home with kitchen granite counter top, back splash upgrades & some stainless steel appliances. Massive first of two double master bedrooms. One featuring a upgraded pedestal sink, slate & tile. Outside features three covered patios, orange tree, grape vines, 15 foot RV gate & 160 foot storage room on huge step down lot below. Portable Jacuzzi with jet, bubbles & self heating element in a shaded gazebo area. Charleston Heights is located at the base of Summerlin Parkway we offer quick & easy access to the 95 freeway.
